        ActorC(Furious)::"OPEN THE DOOR! We know <Actor.he_or_she> is in your house!"
        "What should I do?"
        0:: "Hand <Actor.him_or_her> over"
        1:: money > Prix1:: "Offer to pay a big bribe to the official instead"
        2:: interpersonal + intelligence > 170:: "Threaten to expose the official"
        3:: energy > 25::"Ask for a duel in exchange for <Actor.his_or_her> freedom"
        
        If 0
