            "I easily let <Actor.his_or_her> people in to catch <Actor.him_or_her>, probably to be sent to the corrupt official in no time."
            "They were even happy to with my cooperation enough to pay me a small amount for keep quiet about this dirty arrangement between the tribe and the local government."
            "They were even happy enough with my cooperation so they gave me a small reward of (<Prixl>) to keep quiet about their dirty bizness."
