            Actor.makeInterested(Player)
            Actor:attractiontoplayer += random(10, 30)
            Actor:rapportwithplayer += random(10, 30)
            Actor(Happy):: "Oh my god. You saved me from a lifetime of being a sex slave ... I'm forever in debt to you ... Please, I have nothing to offer you but my virginity ..."
            "What should I say?"
            0:: "Take <Actor.name>'s virginity as my reward"
            1:: "It was only the right thing to do"
            
            If 0
